<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>MissionsAusruf</title>
<meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="IE=11"/>

</head>
<body onload="onload();">
	<img src="data:image/png;base64,"></img>
	<img id="ewald" src="" style="left:50%;top:50%;width:13%;animation:run 30s linear infinite;"></img>
	<img id="buildings" src="data:image/png;base64,"></img>
	<img id="advert" src="" style="width:80%;left:50%;top:100%;transform:translate(-50%,100%);transition:transform 1s;"></img>
	<style id="style">
		*{padding:0;margin:0;}
		html,body{width:100%;height:100%;background-color:rgb(111,160,149);overflow:hidden;}
		img{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;width:100%;}
		#buildings{animation:displace 8s infinite;transform:translate(0,0%);}
		
		@keyframes displace {
		0% {transform:translate(-0.5%,-0.5%);}
		50% {transform:translate(0.5%,0.5%);}
		100% {transform:translate(-0.5%,-0.5%);}
		}
		@keyframes run {
		0% {transform:translate(100%,-40%);}
		50% {transform:translate(70%,-200%);}
		100% {transform:translate(-200%,-250%);}
		}
	</style>
		<script>
		function onload(){
			setTimeout(function(){
				loop();
				setInterval(loop, 12000);
				setInterval(loop2, 300);
			},100);
		}
		var ad1='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad2='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad3='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad4='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad5='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad6='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad7='data:image/png;base64,';
		var ad8='data:image/png;base64,';
		var randomnr=1,randomnrprevious=1,iloop=0;
		function loop(){
			if(iloop==0){randomnr=8;}else{
				if(iloop>8){randomnr=random(1,8);if(randomnrprevious==randomnr){randomnr=random(1,8);}}else{randomnr=iloop;}
			}
			randomnrprevious=randomnr;
			if(randomnr==1){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad1;}
			if(randomnr==2){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad2;}
			if(randomnr==3){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad3;}
			if(randomnr==4){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad4;}
			if(randomnr==5){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad5;}
			if(randomnr==6){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad6;}
			if(randomnr==7){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad7;}
			if(randomnr==8){document.getElementById('advert').src=ad8;}
			document.getElementById('advert').style.transform='translate(-50%,-120%)';
			setTimeout(function(){
				document.getElementById('advert').style.transform='translate(-50%,100%)';
			},8000);
			iloop+=1;if(iloop>10){iloop=1;}
		}
		var frame1='data:image/png;base64,';
		var frame2='data:image/png;base64,';
		var iloop2=1;
		function loop2(){
			if(iloop2==1){document.getElementById('ewald').src=frame1;}
			if(iloop2==2){document.getElementById('ewald').src=frame2;}
			iloop2+=1;if(iloop2>2){iloop2=1;}
		}
		function random(min,max){return Math.floor(Math.random()*(max-min+1)+min)}
	</script>
</body>
</html>
